vote.title: A resolution authorizing (1) the preparation and the payment of future costs and expenses for the issuances of Equipment Acquisition Contractual Obligations, Series 2023 in an amount not to exceed $71,600,000; and (2) an increase in appropriations in the amount not to exceed $6,000,000 in the Equipment Acquisition Contractual Obligations, Series 2023 Fund - Financing: This action has no cost consideration to the City (see Fiscal Information for potential future costs)
